{"id":878,"parent_id":877,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":878,"title":"Daniel 1","subtitle":"","short_title":"Dan.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1","content":[["div",[".title","The Book of",["br"],["span.dominant","Daniel"]],[".titleNumber","Chapter 1"],[".studySummary",["i","Daniel and certain Hebrews are trained in the court of Nebuchadnezzar—They eat plain food and drink no wine—God gives them knowledge and wisdom beyond all others."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.1","order":"02.28.001.58879"},["b","1"],"In the third year of the reign of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Jehoiakim"],"king of Judah came",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Nebuchadnezzar"],"king of Babylon unto Jerusalem, and besieged it."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.2","order":"02.28.001.58880"},["b","2"],"And the Lord gave Jehoiakim king of Judah into his hand, with part of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"vessels"],"of the house of God: which he carried into the land of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"Shinar"],"to the house of his god; and he brought the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"vessels"],"into the treasure house of his god."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.3","order":"02.28.001.58881"},["b","3"],"¶And the king spake unto Ashpenaz",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"the"],"master of his eunuchs, that he should bring",["i","certain"],"of the children of Israel, and of the king’s",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"seed"],", and of the princes;"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.4","order":"02.28.001.58882"},["b","4"],"Children in whom",["i","was"],"no blemish, but",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"well favoured"],", and skilful in all wisdom, and cunning in knowledge, and understanding science, and such as",["i","had"],"ability in them to stand in the king’s palace, and whom they might teach the learning and the tongue of the Chaldeans."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.5","order":"02.28.001.58883"},["b","5"],"And the king appointed them a daily",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"provision"],"of the king’s",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"meat"],", and of the wine which he drank: so nourishing them three years, that at the end thereof they might",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"stand"],"before the king."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.6","order":"02.28.001.58884"},["b","6"],"Now among these were of the children of Judah,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"Daniel"],",",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"Hananiah"],", Mishael, and Azariah:"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.7","order":"02.28.001.58885"},["b","7"],"Unto whom the prince of the eunuchs gave",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"names"],": for he gave unto Daniel",["i","the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"name"]],"of Belteshazzar; and to Hananiah, of Shadrach; and to Mishael, of Meshach; and to Azariah, of Abed-nego."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.8","order":"02.28.001.58886"},["b","8"],"¶But Daniel",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"purposed"],"in his heart that he would not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"defile"],"himself with the portion of the king’s meat, nor with the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"wine"],"which he drank: therefore he requested of the prince of the eunuchs that he might not defile himself."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.9","order":"02.28.001.58887"},["b","9"],"Now God had brought Daniel into",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"favour"],"and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"tender love"],"with the prince of the eunuchs."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.10","order":"02.28.001.58888"},["b","10"],"And the prince of the eunuchs said unto Daniel, I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"fear"],"my lord the king, who hath appointed your meat and your drink: for why should he see your faces",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"worse liking"],"than the children which",["i","are"],"of your",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"sort"],"? then shall ye make",["i","me"],"endanger my head to the king."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.11","order":"02.28.001.58889"},["b","11"],"Then said Daniel to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"Melzar"],", whom the prince of the eunuchs had set over Daniel, Hananiah, Mishael, and Azariah,"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.12","order":"02.28.001.58890"},["b","12"],"Prove thy servants, I beseech thee, ten days; and let them give us",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"pulse"],"to eat, and water to drink."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.13","order":"02.28.001.58891"},["b","13"],"Then let our",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"countenances"],"be looked upon before thee, and the countenance of the children that eat of the portion of the king’s meat: and as thou seest, deal with thy servants."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.14","order":"02.28.001.58892"},["b","14"],"So he consented to them in this matter, and proved them ten days."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.15","order":"02.28.001.58893"},["b","15"],"And at the end of ten days their countenances appeared fairer and fatter in flesh than all the children which did eat the portion of the king’s meat."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.16","order":"02.28.001.58894"},["b","16"],"Thus Melzar took away the portion of their meat, and the wine that they should drink; and gave them pulse."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.17","order":"02.28.001.58895"},["b","17"],"¶As for these four children, God gave them",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"knowledge"],"and skill in all",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"learning"],"and wisdom: and Daniel had",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"understanding"],"in all",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_17d"},"visions"],"and dreams."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.18","order":"02.28.001.58896"},["b","18"],"Now at the end of the days that the king had said he should bring them in, then the prince of the eunuchs brought them in before Nebuchadnezzar."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.19","order":"02.28.001.58897"},["b","19"],"And the king communed with them; and among them all was found none like Daniel, Hananiah, Mishael, and Azariah: therefore stood they before the king."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.20","order":"02.28.001.58898"},["b","20"],"And in all matters of wisdom",["i","and"],"understanding, that the king inquired of them, he found them ten times better than all the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"magicians"],["i","and"],"astrologers that",["i","were"],"in all his realm."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.21","order":"02.28.001.58899"},["b","21"],"And Daniel continued",["i","even"],"unto the first year of king Cyrus."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.1a","order":"02.28.001.58900"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-bondage-of-in-other-lands"},"TG Israel, Bondage of, in Other Lands"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.1b","order":"02.28.001.58902"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/24.1.1-16"},"2 Kgs. 24:1 (1–16)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/36.6.6-10"},"2 Chr. 36:6 (6–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.2a","order":"02.28.001.58904"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/24.13"},"2 Kgs. 24:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.2b","order":"02.28.001.58906"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/11.2"},"Gen. 11:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.2c","order":"02.28.001.58908"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/5.2"},"Dan. 5:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.3a","order":"02.28.001.58910"},["b","3a"],["span.small","OR"],"chief of his officers."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.3b","order":"02.28.001.58912"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/20.18.14-18"},"2 Kgs. 20:18 (14–18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/39.7.3-7"},"Isa. 39:7 (3–7)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.4a","order":"02.28.001.58914"},["b","4a"],["span.small","HEB"],"good in appearance."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.5a","order":"02.28.001.58916"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/31.16"},"2 Chr. 31:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.5b","order":"02.28.001.58918"},["b","5b"],["span.small","HEB"],"delicacies."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.5c","order":"02.28.001.58920"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/10.8"},"1 Kgs. 10:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.6a","order":"02.28.001.58922"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/6.13"},"Dan. 6:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.6b","order":"02.28.001.58924"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/2.17"},"Dan. 2:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.7a","order":"02.28.001.58926"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/2.26"},"Dan. 2:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.7b","order":"02.28.001.58928"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/5.12"},"Dan. 5:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.8a","order":"02.28.001.58930"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/commitment"},"TG Commitment"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.8b","order":"02.28.001.58932"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.3.1-3"},"Hosea 9:3 (1–3)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/word-of-wisdom"},"TG Word of Wisdom"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.8c","order":"02.28.001.58934"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/temperance"},"TG Temperance"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.9a","order":"02.28.001.58936"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/16.7"},"Prov. 16:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.9b","order":"02.28.001.58938"},["b","9b"],["span.small","HEB"],"compassion."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.10a","order":"02.28.001.58940"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/courage"},"TG Courage"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fearful"},"Fearful"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.10b","order":"02.28.001.58942"},["b","10b"],["span.small","IE"],"less healthy."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.10c","order":"02.28.001.58944"},["b","10c"],["span.small","OR"],"age."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.11a","order":"02.28.001.58946"},["b","11a"],["span.small","HEB"],"the steward."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.12a","order":"02.28.001.58948"},["b","12a"],["span.small","IE"],"foods made of seeds, grains, etc.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/9.9.8-9"},"Mosiah 9:9 (8–9)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/89.14"},"D&C 89:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.13a","order":"02.28.001.58950"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/89.18"},"D&C 89:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.17a","order":"02.28.001.58952"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/2.20.20-22"},"Dan. 2:20 (20–22)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/4.8"},"Jacob 4:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/12.9.9-11"},"Alma 12:9 (9–11)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/89.19"},"D&C 89:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.17b","order":"02.28.001.58954"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/education"},"TG Education"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/learn"},"Learn"],"."],["div",{"id":"17c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.17c","order":"02.28.001.58956"},["b","17c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/41.15.1-43"},"Gen. 41:15 (1–43)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/10.1"},"Dan. 10:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"17d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.17d","order":"02.28.001.58958"},["b","17d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vision"},"TG Vision"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.20a","order":"02.28.001.58960"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sorcery"},"TG Sorcery"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/superstitions"},"Superstitions"],"."]]}
